<P>
 Supervisor of Fired Kidder Star Quits: A government bond trading scandal at 
Kidder, Peabody & Co. claimed another victim as the supervisor of the central 
figure in the saga quit, effective immediately. Edward A. Cerullo, executive 
managing director, head of Kidder's fixed-income division and a 15-year veteran 
