(Thanksgiving and memorial) Festival from 1 p.m. to 9 p.m. today and Sunday. 
Performances begin at 3:30 p.m. and will include Taiko drumming, Aikido martial 
arts, a tea ceremony and holiday folk dancing. There will also be games, food, 
