<TEXT>
<P>
 Responding to complaints from residents and business owners, undercover 
sheriff's deputies arrested five women on suspicion of soliciting acts of 
prostitution along Sierra Highway and Palmdale Boulevard in the Antelope 
Valley. 
</P>
<P>
