<P>
CLIPPERS' GAMES AT POND ARE SET 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Charles Barkley, Chris Webber and Karl Malone are expected to be among the 
marquee players performing at The Pond of Anaheim in six games against the 
Clippers in the 1994-95 season. 
</P>
<P>
 The Clippers' first regular season game at The Pond will be Nov. 12 vs. 
Phoenix. Others will be Dec. 15 vs. Golden State; Dec. 17 vs. Dallas; Jan. 21 
vs. Sacramento; March 2 vs. Seattle and April 1 vs. Utah. All are scheduled to 
start at 7:30 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 Tickets are $14, $20, $24, $30, $40, $50 and $100 per game. Ticket packages 
for seven games (including an exhibition against the Lakers) are available. For 
more ticket information, call (213) 748-0500. 
