<HEADLINE>
<P>
WYNETTE, NELSON TO HOST 'COUNTRY MUSIC' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Tammy Wynette and Willie Nelson will host "The Legends of Country Music," a 
weekly series on cable's TNN channel.It premieres Sept. 19. 
</P>
<P>
 Wynette will host the first six episodes, with Nelson taking the next seven. 
TNN says the series will feature each host inviting his or her "favorite 
artists to perform with them and talk about their music." Early guests of 
Wynette's will include Loretta Lynn and Randy Travis. 
</P>
</TEXT>
