<HEADLINE>
<P>
INSIDE & OUT: HAUTE CUISINE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By CYNDI Y. NIGHTENGALE, TIMES STAFF WRITER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Like a Rolls-Royce, a Rolex or court-side season tickets for the Lakers, the 
La Cornue stove is the ultimate. 
</P>
<P>
 La Cornue, a professional French stove, is meticulously crafted. Made of 
hand-polished stainless steel, nickel-plated steel and solid brass, the stove 
has no visible screws for an absolute heat seal. 
</P>
<P>
 One of the two ovens is always gas (for moist cooking and less shrinkage of 
meats and poultry) and the other is always electric (which provides a dry heat 
for pastries, souffles, meringues and breads). 
</P>
<P>
 La Cornue, imported by the Purcell-Murray Co. in Brisbane, Calif., is offered 
in 13 colors, including pistache , a pale shade of green. 
</P>
<P>
 Of course, all of this luxury has a price. 
</P>
<P>
 Just ask the nearly 250 owners -- including actors Danny Glover and Jamie 
Wyeth and comedian Robin Williams -- who have purchased one in the three years 
the stove has been available in the United States. 
</P>
<P>
 For a mere $10,000 to $17,000, depending on the custom features you desire, 
you can add your name to the list. 
</P>
<P>
 For more information or to order, call (800) 892-4040. Resin Wicker 
</P>
<P>
 This furniture can weather the storm -- and then some. 
</P>
<P>
 The newest casual outdoor collection by El Monte-based Brown and Jordan, South 
Bay combines classic contemporary styling with the technology of weatherproof 
materials. 
</P>
<P>
 Resinweave, Brown and Jordan's patented weaving process, involves extruding 
polyolefin resin with ultraviolet inhibitors into wicker or cane. The material 
is handwoven one strand at a time over the aluminum frames of the furniture for 
a wicker-like quality. 
</P>
<P>
 Virtually maintenance-free, the furniture is lightweight, sturdy and 
rustproof, and it will not crack, fade or peel. Thus, you can leave it outside 
all the time, and it will maintain its elegance, rain or shine. 
</P>
<P>
 Included in the line are dining and lounge chairs with cushions, an ottoman, a 
love seat and chaise with cushions and several table styles. Pieces range in 
price from $600 for a chair to $1,700 for a chaise and can be purchased in 
Orange County at Roger's Gardens, Anaheim Patio and La Paz. Under Cover 
</P>
<P>
 Some like it hot. Some like it cold. Some like it in between. 
</P>
<P>
 No matter your preference, when it comes to bedding, the Somma Mattress Co. is 
making it easy to do it your way. 
</P>
<P>
 The EurForma collection, a line of flotation, foam and innerspring mattresses, 
allows you to pick from a choice of zipper tops in foam, wool or down. 
</P>
<P>
 The tops can be mixed or matched for just the right comfort combination. 
</P>
<P>
 "This bedding innovation is comparable to serving up your own good-sleep 
sundae," said Angie Echevarria, president of Somma, which is based in Los 
Angeles. 
</P>
<P>
 The mattresses and tops range in price from about $800 to $1,500. 
</P>
<P>
 To find the nearest Orange County dealer to you, call Charles Falk at (714) 
548-0437, or call (800) 227-6662 for more information. 
</P>
