<P>
BANDIT FLEES S&L, POSSIBLY IN A WIG 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JAIME ABDO 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A robber who may have been wearing a blond wig escaped from Downey Savings and 
Loan with an unknown amount of cash Friday. 
</P>
<P>
 The robber told the teller he had a gun and instructed him to put money in the 
nylon bag he placed on the counter, Huntington Beach Police Lt. Jeff Cope said. 
The robber never displayed a gun, and no one was injured. 
</P>
<P>
