children in the congregation that provides partial scholarships for Jewish 
educational experiences such as Jewish summer camps or trips to Israel, as well 
as for traditional or liberal Jewish schools. 
</P>
<P>
 The decision to offer these scholarships was influenced by the results of a 
study issued by the Jewish Educational Service of North America and Brandeis 
