<TEXT>
<P>
 House identification -- A photograph in Friday's editions was misidentified as 
depicting the Dewey, Ariz., house of suspect John J. Famalaro. The photograph, 
part of a graphic about the Denise Huber murder case, was of the Lake Forest 
home of Famalaro's brother. 
</P>
